@startuml
title Diagram Sekwencji - Pobranie Rankingu Użytkowników (Top Likes)

actor "Klient (Vue 3 / Browser)" as Client
participant "RankingController" as Controller
participant "RankingService" as Service
participant "UserRepository" as Repository
database "SQL Server (EF Core)" as DB

Client -> Controller : GET /api/Ranking/likes?limit=10
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : GetTopByLikesAsync(10)
activate Service

Service -> Repository : GetUsersByMostLikesAsync(10)
activate Repository

Repository -> DB : Złożone zapytanie LINQ\n(Include Pins, Likes,\nOrderByDescending Count, Take 10)
activate DB
DB --> Repository : Lista<User> (wraz z Pins i Likes)
deactivate DB

Repository --> Service : IEnumerable<User>
deactivate Repository

Service -> Service : MapToDto(users)\nWyliczenie TotalLikes i TotalDownloads
activate Service
Service --> Service : IEnumerable<UserRankingDto>
deactivate Service

Service --> Controller : IEnumerable<UserRankingDto>
deactivate Service

Controller --> Client : 200 OK + JSON (Lista UserRankingDto)
deactivate Controller

@enduml
